      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHICKEN KNIGHT (1) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at his last four runs. Last time finished 2nd in a Other on April 19 over 400m at this track behind Zinfandel Dash beaten 2.75 lengths (22.89). Capable of going well again. DANYO'S HENRY (2) flew the lids from out wide with an impressive turn of foot, going on to clock 16.83 when a 1.75 lengths winner over 300m at Murray Bridge Straight last time. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Expecting another bold showing. WITCHER ROSE (4) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing sixth (31.39) in a Grade 6 at Angle Park. Form here sound including six wins. The form out of his last race has been franked. Worth another chance. PAW MANTRA (3) cannot be underestimated.",
